                <run fontalignment='1' fontsize='12' italic='true'>Condition distributions for each dataset, represented by individual heat maps showing relative concentration in each age category. This dashboard is filterable by data source, gender, and age category. </run>
                <run fontalignment='1'>Æ&#10;</run>
                <run fontalignment='1' fontsize='12' italic='true'>Darker orange to red colors indicate a higher concentration of the condition while darker blue colors indicate a lower concentration of the condition. </run>
